{"tid":1867574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓樂天百貨總店因有顧客確診暫停營業","createTime":"2020-02-07T08:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T08:35:41.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b238316a5daca1f85db429c39406a27eccb888f2","tid":1867574,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:30:43.000Z","msg":"南韓至今累計有24宗新型冠狀病毒確診病例，其中一名58歲中國女子，上月23日由武漢入境後行踪不明，直至星期日中午，曾往首爾市明洞的樂天百貨總店購物。樂天百貨因應事件決定暫停營業，對總店徹底採取防疫措施後，在下星期一重新營業。"},{"pid":"71a9eb8d71c21d59d1ac7d214d4da28c39dcb446","tid":1867574,"uid":256952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dQWh5zR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdQWh5zR.jpg&h=4a736a6c&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}